metadata.title: Bering Sea Times Series Data (1996-1999)

creators.name: Atmospheric Research (OAR), Pacific Marine Environmental Laboratory (PMEL)

metadata.description: During the 1996-1999 the following "Times Series Data" were collected: 21  RCM7s, 2  RCM9s, 64  MTRs, 20  Seacats, 3  Pressure guages, 3  SPAAMs 1 Weather bouy , 3024  CTDs
